title: Has the executable object code and its associated PDI files (if any) been produced and loaded into the target hardware for hw/sw integration?
description: Has the executable object code and its associated PDI files (if any) been produced and loaded into the target hardware for hw/sw integration?

title: Is each instantiation of a PDI captured as software life cycle data?
description: Is each instantiation of a PDI captured as software life cycle data?

title: Does the PDI file reference the SAS associated with the executable object code?
description: Does the PDI file reference the SAS associated with the executable object code?

title:
Is the PDI File correct and complete?
  a. Does the PDI comply with the structure defined by the high-level requirements
  b. Does the PDI have the correct value as defined by the high-level requirement (no extra value, no missing value, within range)?
  c. Are related parameter values consistent with each other?
  d. Are all parameter values in alignment with the capabilities of the targeted LRU hardware and Operating System configuration?
  e. Have all parameter values related to the file structure been completely defined?
  f. Do all parameter values trace to high-level requirements and/or justifications for them?

title: Has the the PDI File been independently verified to be correct and complete? (All elements of the PDI have been covered during verification)
